f Tanjung Malim was split from this district to pave the way for [[Muallim District]] which was officiated on 11 January 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bharian.com.my/node/113170 |title=Muallim rasmi menjadi daerah ke-11 di Perak |author=Shamsul Kamal Amarudin |publisher=Berita Harian |date=11 January 2016 |accessdate=2014-09-17}}</ref>\n\n==Administrative divisions==\n[[File:Map of Batang Padang District, Perak.svg|250px|thumb|Map of Batang Padang District]]\nBatang Padang District is divided into 4 [[mukim]]s, which are:<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=http://pdttapah.perak.gov.my/maklumat-korporat/pengenalan/senarai-mukim-dan-statistik-penduduk|title=Laman Web Pejabat Daerah Dan Tanah - Senarai Mukim Dan Statistik Penduduk|first=TAPAH|last=ADMIN|website=pdttapah.perak.gov.my|access-date=2017-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211041805/http://pdttapah.perak.gov.my/maklumat-korporat/pengenalan/senarai-mukim-dan-statistik-penduduk|archive-date=2017-12-11|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* Batang Padang (Tapah town)\n* [[Bidor]]\n* [[Chenderiang]]\n* [[Sungkai]]\n\n== Federal Parliament and State Assembly Seats ==\nList of Batang Padang district representatives in the Federal Parliament ([[Dewan Rakyat]])\n<br />\n{| class=\"toccolours sortable\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! align=\"center\"|Parliament !! Seat Name !! Member of Parliament !! Party\n|-\n! align=\"left\"|P72\n| Tapah || [[Saravanan Murugan|Saravanan A/L Murugan]]|| Perikatan Nasional (BN-MIC)\n|-\n! align=\"left\"|P77\n| Tanjong Malim || [[Chang Lih Kang]] || Pakatan Harapan (PKR)\n|-\n|}\n\n<br />\nList of Batang Padang district representatives in the State Legislative Assembly of Perak\n<br />\n{| class=\"toccolours sortable\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"3\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! align=\"center\"|Parliament !! State !! Seat Name !! State Assemblyman !! Party\n|-\n! align=\"left\"|P72\n|