and)|Cold]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Freak*on*ica]]'' || [[Girls Against Boys]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[gloria!]]'' || [[Gloria Estefan]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[If You See Her]]'' || [[Brooks & Dunn]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[MP Da Last Don]]'' || [[Master P]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Munki]]'' || [[The Jesus and Mary Chain]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Rant and Roar|Rant And Roar]]'' || [[Great Big Sea]] || Compilation\n|-\n| ''[[RFTC]]'' || [[Rocket from the Crypt]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Shut 'Em Down (album)|Shut 'Em Down]]'' || [[Onyx (band)|Onyx]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[The X-Files: The Album]]'' || Various Artists || Soundtrack\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"|8\n| ''[[The Good Will Out]]'' || [[Embrace (English band)|Embrace]] || UK\n|-\n| ''[[Undo the Wicked]]'' || [[Diecast (band)|Diecast]] || Debut\n|-\n| ''[[Peloton (album)|Peloton]]'' || [[The Delgados]] || UK\n|-\n| rowspan=\"12\" align=\"center\"|9\n| ''[[The Devil's Bris]]'' || [[Voltaire (musician)|Voltaire]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Diabolus in Musica]]'' || [[Slayer]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[DLR Band]]'' || [[David Lee Roth]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[F\u266fA\u266f\u221e]]'' || [[Godspeed You Black Emperor!]] || re-issue\n|-\n| ''[[Left of Cool]]'' || [[B\u00e9la Fleck and the Flecktones]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[A Long Way Home]]'' || [[Dwight Yoakam]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Look My Way (Madball album)|Look My Way]]'' || [[Madball]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[My Secret Life (Sonia Dada album)|My Secret Life]]'' || [[Sonia Dada]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Never Say Never (Brandy Norwood album)|Never Say Never]]'' || [[Brandy Norwood|Brandy]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Payton's Place]]'' || [[Nicholas Payton]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Perversion (album)|Perversion]]'' || [[Gravity Kills]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Premonition (John Fogerty album)|Premonition]]'' || [[John Fogerty]] || Live\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|15\n| ''[[Try Whistling This]]'' || [[Neil Finn]] || Solo debut\n|-\n| ''[[Vertical Man]]'' || [[Ringo Starr]] ||-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"10\" align=\"center\"|16\n| ''[[Aaron Carter (album)|Aaron Carter]]'' || [[Aaron Carter]] || US; released in Euro