um)|Media]]'' || [[The Faint]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[*NSYNC (album)|*NSYNC]]'' || [[NSYNC]] || US\n|-\n| ''[[The Pillage]]'' || [[Cappadonna]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Space Heater (album)|Space Heater]]'' || [[Reverend Horton Heat]] ||-\n|-\n| ''Winterland'' || Emma Townhend ||-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|26\n| ''[[The Best of Nick Cave and the Bad Seeds]]'' || [[Nick Cave and the Bad Seeds]] || Compilation\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|30\n| ''[[This Is Hardcore]]'' || [[Pulp (band)|Pulp]] ||-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"9\" align=\"center\"|31\n| ''[[Boggy Depot]]'' || [[Jerry Cantrell]] || LP\n|-\n| ''[[In the Line of Fire (Hussein Fatal album)|In the Line of Fire]]'' || [[Hussein Fatal]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Let's Ride (album)|Let's Ride]]'' || [[Montell Jordan]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Moment of Truth (Gang Starr album)|Moment of Truth]]'' || [[Gang Starr]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[The Ponzi Scheme]]'' || [[Firewater (band)|Firewater]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Night Versions: The Essential Duran Duran]]'' || [[Duran Duran]] || Remix\n|-\n| ''[[Sunburn (Fuel album)|Sunburn]]'' || [[Fuel (band)|Fuel]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[12 Bar Blues (album)|12 Bar Blues]]'' || [[Scott Weiland]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Wishpool]]'' || [[Brother Cane]] ||-\n|-\n|}\n\n===April\u2013June===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\"|Date\n!Album\n!Artist\n!Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"51\" valign=\"center\" align=\"center\" style=\"background:#FFA07A; textcolor:#000;\" | '''A<br>P<br>R<br />I<br />L'''\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|2\n| ''[[www.tism.wanker.com]]'' || [[TISM]] ||-\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"|6\n| ''[[Now That's What I Call Music! 39 (UK series)|Now That's What I Call Music! 39]]'' (UK series) || Various Artists || Compilation\n|-\n| rowspan=\"16\" align=\"center\"|7\n| ''At Rope's End'' || [[New Bomb Turks]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Battle Hymns (Suicide Machines album)|Battle Hymns]]'' || [[The Suicide Machines]] ||-\n|-\n| ''[[Boggy Depot]]'' || [[Jerry Cantrell]] || LP\n|-\n| ''[[Crossroads and Illusions]